name: Insanely Talented Player
author: chena
content: [By Red-Ice Studios, creators of the series ‘Solo Leveling and Omniscient Reader’s Viewpoint’]It’s been six years since the game to decide the fate of the world had started. Hero-King Kang Yoo-Sung, the strongest player who hasn’t dropped from the top ranker’s position once, greets the new season, too.“I… was finished a long fucking time ago. I’m just doing it for the money.”[Taunt Level has drastically increased!][The Elder of Jesters expresses satisfaction with the actions of the contractor!]
